STEERING DOCUMENTATION:
1. INTRO
2. RUNNING CODE
3. SUGGESTIONS
4. EXAMPLE(S)

======================================================
1. INTRO
======================================================
In this directory is are directories containg examples 
of steering files used by:

  MyCrossSection
  MyData
  MyGrid


======================================================
2. RUNNING CODE
======================================================
In general, to run the code:

  ./plot MyCrossSectionSteeringFile.txt

where MyCrossSectionSteeringFile.txt cotnains paths to
a MyData Steering file and a MYGrid steering file.


======================================================
3. SUGGESTIONS
======================================================
Please explore these direcotires in this order:

  MyCrossSectio -> MyData -> MyGrid

then try running the example ( see 4. EXAMPLES(s) )


======================================================
4. EXAMPLE(S)
======================================================
Try running the code with the steering files and grid
in the example/ directory